flowchart TD
  A[Incoming A/B Test + Hypothesis]:::data --> B[Metrics Snapshot / DQ]:::data
  B --> C[Captain]:::captain

  C --> D[Semantic Retrieval Query Builder]:::data
  D --> E[(Vector Database)]:::data
  E --> F[Top-K Similar Experiment IDs]:::data
  F --> G[(Historical Ledger / Structured SoT)]:::data
  G --> H[historical_context_pack]:::obs

  H --> I[Doctor]:::doctor
  I --> J[context_frame gate]:::security
  J --> K[handoff_contract_guard gate]:::security
  K --> L[anti_goodhart_verdict SoT]:::security
  L --> M[Evaluator]:::data
  M --> N[Commander]:::commander
  N --> O[quality_invariants gate]:::security
  O --> P[reasoning_score_policy gate]:::security
  P --> Q[governance_ceiling gate]:::hitl
  Q --> R[verify_acceptance]:::hitl
  R --> S[pre_publish_audit]:::security
  S --> T[Decision Card + Reports]:::obs

  U[(domain_template.json)]:::data --> C
  U --> I
  U --> M
  U --> N

  V[(JSON Contracts + .sha256)]:::security --> J
  V --> K
  V --> L
  V --> O
  V --> P
  V --> Q
  V --> R
  V --> S

  subgraph L1[Scheme 1 Legend]
    LP[PASS]:::pass
    LW[WARN / INCONCLUSIVE]:::warn
    LF[FAIL / BLOCKED / STOP]:::fail
    LH[HOLD_NEED_DATA]:::hold
    LR[RUN_AB]:::runab
    LC[ROLLOUT_CANDIDATE]:::rollout
  end

  classDef data fill:#EAF2FF,stroke:#2563EB,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef captain fill:#E6F7F8,stroke:#0E7490,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef doctor fill:#EAFBF3,stroke:#15803D,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef commander fill:#FFF2E8,stroke:#C2410C,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef hitl fill:#FFF7D6,stroke:#CA8A04,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef security fill:#FFECEC,stroke:#B91C1C,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef obs fill:#F4EEFF,stroke:#7C3AED,color:#0F172A,stroke-width:1.5px;

  classDef pass fill:#EAFBF3,stroke:#16A34A,color:#14532D,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef warn fill:#FFF7D6,stroke:#D97706,color:#7C2D12,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef fail fill:#FFECEC,stroke:#DC2626,color:#7F1D1D,stroke-width:1.5px;
  classDef hold fill:#FFF2E8,stroke:#C2410C,color:#7C2D12,stroke-width:1.5px;
